data.current_description: Directly uploads a Yum artifact. The returned Operation will complete once the resources are uploaded. Package, Version, and File resources are created based on the imported artifact. Imported artifacts that conflict with existing resources are ignored.
data.summary_suggestion: Upload a Yum artifact directly to repository
data.description_suggestion: Directly uploads a Yum (RPM) artifact to the specified repository. The operation accepts a Yum artifact file and creates corresponding Package, Version, and File resources. Returns a long-running Operation that completes once the artifact is processed and stored.
